title: Cay Bo De
description: Offers a traditional breakfast noodle soup of My Tho called hu tieu chay as well other soups. It has evolved considerably over the years, and now has 3 separate dining rooms in 3 separate store fronts, with a fourth, the original location, serving all 3. The current addresses are 22, 24, 32 and 36 Nam Ky Khoi Nghia. It's all one restaurant.
